properties.Name: EmployeeTelephoneNumber
properties.Description: The employee telephone number of the associated Telephone Number Type for the indicated period.

Columns.Name: EmployeeId

Columns.Name: TelephoneNumber

Columns.Name: PeriodStartTimestamp

Columns.Name: PeriodEndTimestamp

Columns.Name: EmployeeTelephoneNumberNote
Columns.Description: A note, comment or additional information regarding the Telephone Number.

Columns.Name: LocationId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Location.

Columns.Name: TextCapableIndicator
Columns.Description: Indicates whether the phone is capable of receiving text messages.
